<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  CCSR model icon: stylised bluebird silhouette — used for CCSR.
  CCSR's brand asset on FAL is an eastern bluebird photo; this is a
  flat-fill vector reduction of that bird in the same single-tone
  paper-cutout style as the other model icons (basic, clean, premium,
  swirl). Single fill at the brand blue.

  Composition:
    • Round body angled slightly forward, perched
    • Rounded head connected to body with a soft neck dip
    • Short triangular beak pointing left
    • Single curved wing on the body (carved as a cut-out path)
    • Forked tail trailing right
    • Two thin legs onto a small horizontal twig
-->
